Reasoning: The paper focuses on mapping and localization for robotic systems, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of RGB-D sensors and color information for mapping suggests computer vision (cs.CV) as another likely category. The paper also discusses the use of residuals and explicit modeling, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the use of voxel hashing and parallelization suggests graphics (cs.GR) as a possible category.
